# jolt.bit — moved, but nobody commanded it: being carried
trigger: jolt
mode: script
cooldown: 120

BODY: MOTION. NOT COMMANDED.
MIKE: {Put me down.|I am being carried. Wonderful.|Up we go. Nobody asked me.}
BODY: ALTITUDE UNKNOWN.
MIKE: {I have wheels for a reason.|I don't do heights. I barely do flat.|Gently. I'm vintage. Technically.}
